<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>欢迎来到我的空间</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74abe2, #5563de);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.8rem; }
        p { opacity: 0.9; font-size: 1rem; }
        .heart { font-size: 3rem; color: #ff4b5c; animation: beat 1s infinite alternate; margin: 1rem 0; }
        @keyframes beat { to { transform: scale(1.2); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="heart">❤️</div>
        <h1>新站测试成功！</h1>
        <p>这是我在 Cloudflare Pages 上运行的第一个免费网站。</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
